---
title: My Big Fat Greek Chicken Salad with Marinated Tomato & Lemon Tahini Dressing
description: Looking for delicious lunch or dinner ideas? That’s what’s in store with this salad, made with pre-measured, high-quality ingredients. Much like the Portokalos family in the rom-com, this salad is more boisterous than the typical Greek salad. It starts with a big bowl of crisp lettuce tossed with juicy lemon-shallot marinated tomato, fresh cukes, and savory-spiced chicken. It’s all drizzled with a creamy garlic-lemon-tahini Greek vinaigrette. Light and satisfying–it’s a match made in heaven.
